9da44afb41df14a76c24936085e0581fb6c07e05.commit.message:
Install.jsp received the Stripes treatment and moved to admin/Installer.jsp. Key new features include the ability to configure and test LDAP user/role lookups dynamically via AJAX. Additional security configuration enhancements are planned, for example JavaMail live config/testing. InstallActionBean also features "instant setup" -- changes can be applied WITHOUT restarting the webapp.
